<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="id903cab1d-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="id903cab1e-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective <date date="1979-10-01">Oct. 1, 1979</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/96/53/s512/a">section 512(a) of Pub. L. 96–53</ref>, set out as an Effective Date of 1979 Amendment note under <ref href="/us/usc/t22/s2151">section 2151 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
